-- Bernanke Said to Plan Semiannual Policy Testimony on Feb. 26
-- B y   P e t e r   C o o k   a n d   J o s h u a   Z u m b r u n
-- 2013-02-04T17:55:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-04/bernanke-said-to-plan-semiannual-policy-testimony-on-feb-26.html
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S. Bernanke  is scheduled to give his semi-annual testimony on
monetary policy before the Senate Banking Committee on Feb. 26,
according to a committee aide.  The Fed chairman testifies before the Senate Banking
Committee and the House Financial Services Committee of Congress
in two-day hearings twice a year. The hearings are typically
held in February and July. The testimony is scheduled to begin
at 10 a.m., the aide said today on condition of anonymity.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Joshua Zumbrun  in Washington at 
 jzumbrun@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story: Christopher
Wellisz at   cwellisz@bloomberg.net  